# script-src hashes whitelist the page's inline <script> snippets:
#   1) Organization JSON-LD (every page, sitewide in Base.astro)
#   2) Mobile-menu close-on-click handler (every page, in Header.astro)
#   3) Astro's IntersectionObserver loader (client:visible bootstrap)
#   4) Astro's astro-island custom-element registration
#   5) SoftwareApplication JSON-LD (homepage only, in index.astro)
#   6) the homepage's cinematic behaviour bundle (scroll-reveal IO + lazy
#      hero aerial loop), which Astro inlines because it has no imports.
# Regenerate after an Astro version bump OR after editing any of:
#   - src/scripts/cinematic.ts
#   - src/layouts/Base.astro (the Organization JSON-LD)
#   - src/pages/index.astro (the SoftwareApplication JSON-LD)
#   - src/components/Header.astro (the mobile-menu handler)
